    "description": "The setting is a  railroad shrine.<br>Choose one of the four apostles and off you go!<br><br>At the base location, you will mainly collect and manufacture materials by leaving the game alone.<br>Once materials are gathered, head into the adventure and use them to break through!<br><br>As you progress in your adventures, <br>you will have more friends to support you and you will be able to play side contents.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Various functions and contents]</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Basic functions to move around in JRPG style.<br></li><li>The base that gradually becomes more advantageous and convenient by acquiring treasures.<br></li><li>Unexplored areas that can be played by acquiring maps.<br></li><li>A group of people who will join you and help you in your base.<br></li><li>A challenging side trip area.<br></li><li>Extended areas that continue even after the main story is completed.<br></li><li>Endless looping content.<br></li><li>Random dungeon-like content<br></li><li>Support for Achievements</li></ul><br>More to come in the future!<br><strong>★Even a simple base at first becomes more and more luxurious as you acquire treasures!<br>★Seasonal event areas and more!</strong>",
